title: Adding Sugar to Water
description: An illustration showing a hand holding a spoon with a scoop of sugar above a glass of water. The glass is transparent and contains clear water, with a shadow cast on the surface beneath it.

title: Pouring Water into a Bottle
description: An illustration showing a hand pouring water from a glass into a red funnel, which is placed on top of a bottle. The funnel directs the water into the bottle.

title: Ant
description: An illustration of an ant, showcasing its segmented body, six legs, and antennae. The ant has a reddish-brown coloration and is depicted in a side view.

title: Crumpled Foil Packet
description: A crumpled, shiny foil packet with a camouflage pattern, resembling a used or discarded wrapper. The packet is flat but has uneven edges, indicating it has been crumpled.
